# CHATSTORY V2 MASTER SPECIFICATION

## Memory Preservation Platform

---

# PROJECT VISION

ChatStory is NOT an AI summarizer.

ChatStory is a memory preservation platform.

Users are not uploading years of conversations because they want a short summary.

Users are uploading conversations because they want to preserve memories, relive meaningful moments, revisit milestones, and keep important stories alive.

The system must optimize for:

✓ Memory Preservation

✓ Event Coverage

✓ Story Quality

✓ Emotional Value

✓ Trust

✓ Simplicity

NOT:

✗ Fast Summaries

✗ Aggressive Compression

✗ Minimal Token Usage

✗ One-PDF Outputs

Good things take time.

The system should prefer quality over speed whenever possible.

---

# USER EXPERIENCE PHILOSOPHY

The application should feel like:

"We are carefully crafting something meaningful."

Not:

"We are running an AI tool."

Every screen, notification and message should reinforce:

* Memories matter
* Stories deserve care
* Processing takes time because quality matters
* Users are creating something valuable

