# TERMS & CONDITIONS MODAL

Checkboxes are not sufficient.

Before upload:

Display mandatory popup modal.

Users cannot continue until accepted.

Contents:

* User owns uploaded content or has permission.
* AI will process uploaded chats.
* Outputs may contain inaccuracies.
* Uploaded chats deleted after 24 hours.
* Service not responsible for disputes.
* Service not responsible for emotional, financial, legal, personal, social or reputational consequences.
* User accepts AI-generated interpretation.

Buttons:

[I Agree And Continue]

[Cancel]

No upload without acceptance.

---

# DATA RETENTION POLICY

Uploaded chats:

Delete automatically after 24 hours.

Temporary processing files:

Delete automatically after 24 hours.

Retain only:

* Generated outputs
* Job metadata
* Payment metadata

Retention periods configurable.

